name: Brangus Glee (V)
Lore: 'Elder of a dextrous race of renowned travelers. Gambler. Frequents casinos, bars and spaceports. Originally from distant planet Dor Nameth',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots.  Deploys -1 and forfeit +1 at a docking bay or aboard a starship.  During your control phase, if at a battleground, may use 1 force (free if at Casino) to exchange a card in hand with a random card in Lost Pile.  Immune to attrition < 3.(Original concept by Bill Kafer - League Cube Tournament 2009)',
